@startuml
title Architecture Diagram

left to right direction

package "Sensors" as Sensors
package "Embedded\n(Raspberry Pi)" as Embedded
package "Frontend" as Frontend
package "Admin Frontend" as Admin
package "Backend API\n(/api/v1)" as Backend {
  [/telemetry]
  [/logs]
  [/devices]
  [/rooms]
  [/sensors]
  [/users]
}
package "Database\n(MongoDB)" as DB

Sensors  -right[hidden]-> Embedded
Embedded -right[hidden]-> Frontend
Frontend -right[hidden]-> Admin
Admin    -right[hidden]-> Backend
Backend  -right[hidden]-> DB

Sensors  --> Embedded : POST (readings), PUT (device, sensor)
Embedded --> Backend  : POST (telemetry), PUT (device, sensor)
Frontend --> Backend  : GET (room)
Admin    --> Backend  : GET/PUT/POST/DELETE
Backend  --> DB       : GET/PUT/POST/DELETE

@enduml
